dc_title_s: Dugong Sites and Dolphin Schools on the Eastern Coast of Kenya, 1998
dc_description_s: This dataset portrays locations of dugong sites (an herbivorous marine mammal related to the manatee) and dolphin schools on the eastern coast of KenyaThis data was used in Map 6.4 and Map 6.5 in Nature's Benefits in Kenya: An Atlas of Ecosystems and Human Well-Being.
